        "Data": [
          "==Applies To==\n\n* PCI DSS Requirement 8.1.8\n\n==Policy Statement==\n\nLock idle sessions.\n\n==Policy Purpose==\n\nLocking inactive sessions ensures that a passerby cannot use the credentials of the user who is currently logged in.\n\n==Related Guidance==\n\n* [[930f62d1-cce9-4277-b726-551ca551a275|Lock Idle Sessions]]\n\n==Related Checklist Items==\n\n* [[30481d98-954a-4599-8f45-931a842f5541|Idle Sessions Are Locked]]"
